        <list-item>
          <p>R-loops = set of identified R-loop regions,</p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>500 bp <italic toggle="yes">W</italic> = 500 bp sliding window located in spKAS-seq peaks,</p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>plus-reads (<italic toggle="yes">W</italic>) = number of spKAS-seq reads mapped to the plus strand in 500 bp window,</p>
        </list-item>
        <list-item>
          <p>minus-reads (<italic toggle="yes">W</italic>) = number of spKAS-seq reads mapped to the minus strand in 500 bp window,</p>
